-- ============================================================
-- Batch 25 — 25 AI-NATIVE tools across under-covered categories
-- (Step 41 — scale to 1,500). First batch shipped under the
-- new AI-relevance gate (codified 2026-04-27): every tool here
-- is either AI-native or ships AI as a headline feature.
--
-- Categories (5 each):
--   A. AI sales: Cresta, Nooks, Sybill, 11x, Second Nature
--   B. AI legal: Robin AI, EvenUp, Alexi, Lexis+ AI, BriefCatch
--   C. AI healthcare scribes: Heidi Health, Freed, Augmedix,
--      Corti, DeepScribe
--   D. AI agents/employees: Lindy, MultiOn, Ema, Cassidy,
--      Stack AI
--   E. AI customer support: Decagon, Sierra, Moveworks,
--      Cognigy, Ada
--
-- Drafted via 5 parallel research agents (5 tools each), each
-- verifying canonical URL + 2025/2026 pricing tiers via
-- WebFetch. Affiliate metadata stays in the affiliate master
